1. No task starts before dependencies complete
2. Running tasks' total resourceCost <= totalResources
3. Running tasks count <= maxConcurrency
4. makespan = max(entry.endTime)
5. order lists task IDs sorted by startTime (ties: priority desc, ID asc)
